Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了 说笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是与我紧紧地缠绕的话不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.84,0:21:47.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.35,0:21:53.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.72,0:21:58.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.02,0:22:04.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.31,0:22:07.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&Hdc\3a&Hdc\4a&Hdc}Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.36,0:22:17.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.25,0:22:28.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.96,0:22:36.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能   太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.35,0:22:42.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.76,0:22:53.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.03,0:00:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是传说的解决篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诡计和证据都是意料之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.41,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们因为旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到一个有五重塔的幻块寺参观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是寺庙与开发公司有些纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后隔天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.45,0:01:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开发公司的社长 小田英明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.20,0:01:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现吊死在五重塔的塔顶前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.04,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五重塔的传说一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.10,0:02:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的第一现场就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的假设是正确的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生不是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人大概就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候讲了那句话的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔传说 (后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.02,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在这里做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 掉在这里的领带夹不是小田先生的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小田先生的领带夹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面镶着钻石的领带夹并不是常有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生 我想你来确认一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是社长的领带夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.88,0:03:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 还敢说我们偷东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想钱包也掉在那附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如查清楚一点再下结论吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样小田先生并没有遇到强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.08,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是在自杀的时候不小心让领带夹掉在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里距离五重塔有几十公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自杀的时候掉下来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得距离太远了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是这样掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生懊恼着该不该在这里自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就在那时候不小心掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.51,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是领带夹不是那么容易就可以掉落的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的手肘那里有草迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领带夹不是掉在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些草迹是在这里沾到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.23,0:04:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.16,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生果然是在这里和某人起纷争而倒下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要把小田先生的尸体放下来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子好像不够长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小田先生的脚无法站在栏杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小田先生放下来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脚站不到栏杆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多相差五十公分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不站在栏杆上面拉住绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么自杀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 这点你怎么解释呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.96,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生在懊恼着要不要自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后爬到五重塔上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.53,0:04:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算少了五十公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地步不想死也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是跳上去吊颈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有很多状况证明是他杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就算是他杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.62,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这就必须有人背着失去意识的小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.41,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过那些狭窄的通道到顶楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在五重塔上面和小田先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有这些迹象出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要如何将小田先生吊在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个短了五十公分的圈圈里面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样越是证明他杀的可能性越低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.94,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生如果不是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无法吊在五重塔塔顶的前端的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.38,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们已经有了结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.98,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要用人为的力量去改变天罚再等一百年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点夹着尾巴滚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的确有几个疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过却没有可以推翻他是自杀的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小田先生的确是被人杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是如何将小田先生吊在五重塔的前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无法解开这个谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个案件就会被当作自杀来处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是绑在栏杆上面的绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是活结呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个谜底终于解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用这个方法的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以把绳子绑在栏杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 不可以乱碰那些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推理没有错误的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西应该还在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.32,0:07:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想犯人一定是用这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.25,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小田先生变成自杀的样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还有新的摩擦过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报应啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.53,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然假借传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种诡计杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只剩下证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找出那个人做的证据才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是一个另类自杀 不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在总算破案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我却觉得这个案子好像有什么疑点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还这样子讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就在报告书上面写说是因为报应而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样写的话 我会被革职的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.15,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回酒店去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那些员工一定很心急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 请先留下联络地址和电话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在酒店里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 这么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请联络这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生好像带了不少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该不会是小田先生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和社长的钱包形状和颜色完全不一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.96,0:09:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天要发给员工的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的 我是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要吓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小田已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么主题公园的计划应该就无效了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在不马上中止的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司就会倒闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.52,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这座寺庙的所有权应该也可以归还了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.85,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份所有权社长已经交给我来保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想现在还给你们应该是最好的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 淡海大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我看错你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.66,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.59,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这份所有权也是一个误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就再替小田念个经吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当他最后做了一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也可以放心回到总寺院继续修行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出发的话…傍晚就可以到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去整理一下五重塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能不承认的…那决定性的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横沟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.87,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事件一定是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果毛利先生这样讲的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就被人给吵醒 害我现在好想睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回酒店再睡一觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 睡虫突然出现…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.48,0:11:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将钮扣型扩音器放在大叔的额头上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这是个自杀案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以结案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横沟警官 真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经出现不少提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么还是不明白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你现在才讲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我认为你应该可以自己发现到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我太迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让我表演一个推理秀给大家看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里 横沟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想做一个实验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以请那些警官帮个忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们马上去做准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先将一个和小田先生重量相当的袋子放在草地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袋口用绳子绑住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.78,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那条绳子绕到五重塔的五楼屋顶的前端上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后通过栏杆再延伸到地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑到现在已经不用的水井上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.21,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再将绳子绑在那些钢铁上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压在一条很容易掉下去的铁棒上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 横沟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.62,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用力拉一下那条绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊…吊上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小田先生一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这次报应的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子上面烧焦的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为挂在屋顶前端上经过强力的摩擦而成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一条新的绳子摩擦过后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会出现这种现象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而领带夹掉落的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就是犯罪的第一现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犯人是如何将绳子套到小田先生的颈部的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生也会做抵抗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并没有发现他被殴打过的痕迹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这是最大的疑点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我重新说明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先犯人利用手机将小田先生叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.13,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再找机会将绳子套到小田先生的颈部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时拉动绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.86,0:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让钢铁掉到井里面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生在被绳子拉上去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以将绳子从颈部上拿开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.93,0:14:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以犯人就用脚绊倒小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.34,0:14:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是像小田先生这样的人也很容易在不注意中被绊倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小田先生手肘上的草迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这个时候沾到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领带夹也是在这个时候掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后小田先生在还没解开绳子之前就已经被拉上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的确是倒下了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.86,0:15:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚跟的地方就不会有泥巴的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成这个事件是很多人一起做的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.09,0:15:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你终于发现这个问题了 横沟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小田先生是个一百公斤巨型身材的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人独自一个人想把绳子绑在栏杆上面的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.62,0:15:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无法拉动绳子 所以只能握住绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在切断绳子的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子就会被拉过去 从手中滑落啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一个人的话怎么可能把绳子绑到栏杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一个人犯案的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在通过栏杆的那条绳子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了一个活结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在绳子中间打了个圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.32,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经叫五重塔上面的警官这样做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫他们试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绳子切断绑在栏杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.94,0:16:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先将活结绕到栏杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.89,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后拿棒子穿过那个圈圈成为一个定点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把外面的绳子给割断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将割断的绳子穿过圈圈再绑起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把棒子抽掉就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横沟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把绳子绑在栏杆上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一个人就可以做到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是把割断的绳子给拉回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢到古井里面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.33,0:16:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样利用传说而设计出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小田先生看起来像自杀的计划就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想犯人唯一的失误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.35,0:17:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让小田先生的脚差五十公分才能站在栏杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这点我才会怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生并不是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够做到这种事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.94,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了寺庙的人之外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的意思是说犯人就是我们其中一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.33,0:17:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用诡计杀害小田先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.43,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡说什么啊 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这间寺庙一点都不清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是ODA酒店的经理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是ODA观光的高级职员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装说为了要建造主题公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以拿到寺庙的蓝图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以很轻易地知道五重塔的高度和古井的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要工人将钢铁放在古井附近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这次的杀人计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的…的确是我叫人这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算是我叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是工作上需要用到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且毛利先生也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我出差去了 根本不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.76,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道小田先生和春海先生昨晚的争吵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来到这里的时候这样子讲过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为知道昨天的争吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方要用法律方式来解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以非常担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春海先生是昨晚才回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好和你错过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你为什么会知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…社长告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在东京的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长打手机给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实是在手机里面听到这件事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.38,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是在为了杀害小田先生而把他叫来这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说我是犯人 证据拿出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚还在这里的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据就在你身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个决定性的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看看尾村先生的钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以拿出来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是说钱上面有社长的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是社长给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不能证明什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 证据在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在纸币里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是ODA酒店的收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九月十二日 十九点四十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是购买雪茄的收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.54,0:19:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.28,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是昨晚我们和小田先生一起吃饭的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生收下的收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在那之前就离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后没有再见过小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的收据会在你的钱包里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.66,0:20:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀害小田先生之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现钱包掉在草地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以决定顺手牵羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发觉纸币里面夹着一张收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.14,0:20:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果调查一下那张收据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面应该也有小田先生的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底如何 尾村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不承认吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种事之下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的动机到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了逃税
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司的经营开始走下坡路的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.27,0:21:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长要我做逃税的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.73,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个 我也收到不少好处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这是社长为了预防被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候要我背上所有的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会给了我这么多的好处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.39,0:21:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才对小田先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想趁着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替公司做了这么多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.79,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来却像蜥蜴一样尾巴被切掉之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.17,0:23:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有一个旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.71,0:23:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只要和爸爸在一起都会有事件出现呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.30,0:23:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.23,0:23:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是爸爸被诅咒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好来庙里玩 趁机将那厄运给赶走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.67,0:23:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.42,0:23:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个侦探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.06,0:23:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探当然要有事件发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.93,0:23:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是粮食的来源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.78,0:23:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外就是我的生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.69,0:23:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做名侦探的就是不断会有事件来挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.13,0:23:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.44,0:23:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的确是个多意外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.83,0:23:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.75,0:24:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是新一的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.87,0:24:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.93,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.92,0:24:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S SPECIAL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.70,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中的密室 工藤新一首次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.97,0:24:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晕车药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.65,0:24:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次是特别篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.56,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.62,0:24:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没登场的家伙 喝～
